== Welcome to Kakeibo Sanataro
Sanataro - Simple Web Household Account Book.
 built with Ruby on Rails 3.2.

== Features
* Simple kakeibo Web Application.
* Multi-User Support. (But no collaboration feature)
* Simple input User-Interface for iPhone.
* See more on a demo page. http://k.nu-chon.org

== Requirement
* Ruby: MRI (>= 1.9.2)
* Rails: Rails 3.2
* DB: MySQL or PostgreSQL (heroku available)

== FIXME / TODO
This software has been upgrade from Rails-2.1, 2.2, 2.3, 3.0, 3.1 to 3.2 escalatorily, so there are lots of points of old fassion expressions to be fixed.
* There are some points where Object-Oriented model is corrupted. They should be fixed.(especially, entities_controller.rb)
* There are some places where hard-coded Japanese characters.
* Fixture dependency should be removed and replaced with other framework(FactoryGirl, Fabrication, etc)
* Now, there is no view specs and cucumber senarios.

